{"tid":2412713,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"油麻地避風塘發現2隻黑天鵝","createTime":"2021-02-18T07:43:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T08:29:25.000Z","uid":234553,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0391f91188fad7bff6f952a9b4e7cfbc9dedc766","tid":2412713,"uid":234553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T07:43:35.000Z","msg":"黑天鵝現身油麻地避風塘！有東網讀者今晨(18日)約9時，在避風塘卸貨區附近公眾碼頭發現2隻黑天鵝蹤影，當時該對天鵝正在一樓梯位置徘徊。據東網讀者表示，約10日前已發現該對天鵝在避風塘出現，有工人指卸貨區一帶海面經常有貨輪往來，恐會對2隻黑天鵝構成危險。<br />\n翻查漁農自然護理署《香港鳥類名錄》，黑天鵝並非本地物種，相信該對黑天鵝從其他地方飛來香港。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210218/photo/bkn-20210218092553336-0218_00822_001_01b.jpg?20210218152634\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20210218%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210218092553336-0218_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20210218152634&h=b9eea40b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc1f67b8b5f4d48179a103d8311225a69b94ba2a","tid":2412713,"uid":275498,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T07:44:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔怪得跌啦"},{"pid":"3589ec167bd1aa1849be27edb139815ed87ac031","tid":2412713,"uid":25858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cc1f67b8b5f4d48179a103d8311225a69b94ba2a","tid":2412713,"uid":275498,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T07:44:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔怪得跌啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T07:53:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"983327ee4ea45618297e0ba1275d07f6de8926e6","tid":2412713,"uid":30274,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cc1f67b8b5f4d48179a103d8311225a69b94ba2a","tid":2412713,"uid":275498,"like":3,"dislike":3,"s